description:
REWARDING GAMEPLAY

Demanding challenges, new traps and mechanics are easy to grasp but hard to master. Find a way to gather all of the coins and become the best hacker.

STYLISH GRAPHICS

Enjoy the 8 bit graphics of Cyber Protocol. The neon lighting, simple shapes and overall cyberpunk aesthetic, will guide you on your path.

GREAT MUSIC

Sit back and listen to the soundtracks. Cyber Protocol has some of the best 80's styled music that gaming has to offer.

Key Features:

- Zone A of Cyber Protocol
- Unlimited playtime
- Cyberpunk mixed with an 8 bit aesthetic
name: Cyber Protocol Prologue
intro: Embark on a mission to save Android (G0X6). Cyber Protocol Prologue includes Zone A of the full Cyber Protocol experience.
